slide.css
body{
margin: 0;
padding: 0;
background: #313131;
}
.slider{
      width: 800px;
      height: 400px;
      background: url();
      margin:100px auto;
      animation: slide  20s infinite;
}
@keyframes slide{
      25%{
      background: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);
      }
      50%{
      background: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);
      }
      75%{
      background: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);
      }
      80%{
      background: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);
      }
      100%{
      background: url(https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSiYEll4DbhG-a3ymWVax-ykX4Z2-rRtYNZ3g&usqp=CAU);

}
